                <a href="/news/american-sociological-association-book-award">
                 <h3>
                  American Sociological Association Book Award
                 </h3>
                </a>
                Dr. Rosemary Hopcroft's 2016 book, Evolution and Gender: Why It Matters for Contemporary Life received the 2018 best book award by the Evolution, Biology &amp; Society Section of the American Sociological Association.
